    "long_instructions": "# AI-Driven Encryption  \r\n\r\nThis chatbot has been fine-tuned to provide insights into **AI-Driven Encryption** and its role in cybersecurity.  \r\n\r\n## **Do This:**  \r\n\r\n### Explore AI in Security (Activity)\r\n- Interact with the chatbot to understand how **AI-Driven Encryption** works and how it helps protect sensitive data.  \r\n- Use the **Conversation Starters** below to guide your exploration:  \r\n   - **Solution Overview:** *How does AI-Driven Encryption work?*  \r\n   - **Problem Addressed:** *What network vulnerabilities does it target?*  \r\n   - **Pros & Cons:** *What are the advantages and limitations of this solution?*  \r\n   - **Project Application:** *How could this be used to mitigate risks in my chosen company scenario?*  \r\n\r\n### Risk Assessment Application \r\n- Use the chatbot’s responses to refine your **Network Security Risk Assessment** by identifying how AI-Driven Encryption could help **secure, encode, and protect** sensitive data from cyber threats.  \r\n\r\n### Tip: \r\n- If the chatbot’s response is unclear, try **rephrasing your question** with more details for a **more targeted answer**.  \r\n",
