          "Healthcare Data Security (MediSure Health Systems)\n\nEncrypts electronic health records to prevent patient data leaks.\nUses AI to detect unauthorized access attempts and re-encrypt data.\n",
          "Banking & Financial Transactions (FinTrust Banking Solutions)\n\nProtects customer transactions and financial data with AI-enhanced encryption.\nUses AI to automatically rotate encryption keys to prevent breaches.",
          "IoT Security in Robotics (NovaTech Robotics)\n\nEncrypts communication between IoT-connected robots to prevent tampering.\nUses AI to adjust encryption strength based on detected security threats.",
          "User Data Protection in Streaming Services (StreamView Entertainment)\n\nSecures customer login credentials and payment details through AI-enforced encryption.\nDetects suspicious account activity and automatically re-encrypts compromised accounts.",
          "Examples of Good Responses:\nHow does AI-Driven Encryption work?\n\n\"AI-Driven Encryption uses machine learning to automatically encrypt sensitive data and adjust encryption keys based on security risks. It ensures data stays protected, even if attackers breach a system.\"\nWhat vulnerabilities does it address?\n\n\"This method helps prevent data leaks, unauthorized access, and weak encryption keys by continuously monitoring threats and strengthening encryption when needed.\""
